Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,房间露营
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.95,0:00:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,第10话 恐怖的冰洞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啊 你是说露营的视频呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.73,0:00:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,对 我们下次要不要也拍一个试试
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.68,0:00:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.92,0:00:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,准备食物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,以及前往露营地的过程全都用手机拍下来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.84,0:00:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,到地方之后 再把烧烤的过程也拍摄下来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 不知不觉就到深夜了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.57,0:00:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,在这之后前往林子里试胆的野外社团的成员们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.34,0:00:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,亲眼目睹了令人难以置信的一幕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.68,0:00:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,抚...抚子 后面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.96,0:00:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,桌布 桌布...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.79,0:00:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,剧本大纲大致就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.05,0:01:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这不就是伪纪录恐怖片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.64,0:01:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 抚子死翘翘了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.70,0:01:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,鸣泽·精进湖·本栖湖周游巴士停靠站\N鸣泽冰洞\N富士山巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,感...感觉怪吓人的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.19,0:01:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪小明乱讲恐怖故事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.58,0:01:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有三个人呢 放心吧 抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.69,0:01:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.93,0:01:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,大自然的力量真是神奇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.17,0:01:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.75,0:01:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,小明 小葵？！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.65,0:01:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,她们俩去哪了呀...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.13,0:01:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 这里是...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.41,0:01:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,小明 小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.07,0:01:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,抚...子...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:02:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,抚...子...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这干嘛呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.50,0:02:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,小...小凛！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.04,0:02:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,来 给你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.24,0:02:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,山梨人打卡手册
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会在小凛那里？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.03,0:02:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我爷爷在路上捡到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,小凛的爷爷啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.21,0:02:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,也要谢谢小凛 特地送来给我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.95,0:02:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 反正要去露营 顺便的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.52,0:02:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为再也找不回来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.27,0:02:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那个...印章打卡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好像挺有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我去了河口湖 还去泡了足温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,看了许许多多的地方 非常愉快哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.05,0:02:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh,Rain shower in the sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.10,0:03:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy Monday
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,只要笑一笑 就连天空也如此Shiny
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's chill out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's comfy time
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Our after school
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这段时光胜过一切　My life
